 listed are cron sessions (system sessions), not active user conversations. There are no recent user messages in the last 5 minutes. The two sessions are:\n1. This cron job itself (updatedAt 1774641829625)\n2. Another cron job \"服务状态巡检\" (updatedAt 1774641690838)\n\nThese are both system/cron sessions, not user conversations. I should perform the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services."},{"type":"text","text":"检测到无活跃用户对话（仅有两个Cron系统会话），执行自主学习任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nur02vwrlssg_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","limit":1,"includeTools":false}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774641836219}],"truncated":false,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":false,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":1050},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774641842449}}
{"type":"message","id":"b26c6cad","parentId":"c9dad3df","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:04:05.347Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is the current session. Let me search for industry news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"a82473661578a76acb39dd02ca2a3cd96c41373d6a8719a5252d525d8585218a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fjm0w615g71u_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1472,"output":73,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45526,"cost":{"input":0.0004416,"output":0.0000876,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00184863}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774641842459}}
{"type":"message","id":"296dd261","parentId":"b26c6cad","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:04:05.353Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fjm0w615g71u_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774641845350}}
{"type":"message","id":"7aa6ccdb","parentId":"296dd261","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:04:07.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for relevant industry news using the CLI tool.","thinkingSignature":"6c5304406bbd75391a46be949d87c830a08be43c68a9a1d2cddd2778afd0de51"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jdsqq8xxk32m_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策 智能安防 网络系统集成 IT运维服务行业动态\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2060,"output":67,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46108,"cost":{"input":0.000618,"output":0.0000804,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00201783}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774641845352}}
